{"tid":19520,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［多字慎入］帶住菲林機去旅行 - 四國高松","createTime":"2016-12-02T23:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T07:36:55.000Z","uid":21385,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"381d660f69157dd5d48915b686af46ecea4231f6","tid":19520,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"轉會lihkg前同囡囡去佐轉四國幾日，影佐少少相分享下啦<br />\n<br />\n頭幾日冇咩地方去因為一落機就冷親同埋個天陰陰地，都係淨係係高松附近行下，當然有去栗林公園啦唔洗問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065148_9cb0c15f10b81d4effe8d3b253680eed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065148_9cb0c15f10b81d4effe8d3b253680eed.jpg&h=a749dde2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065148_5d1acbcc0762f62e02ead752ac9a0076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065148_5d1acbcc0762f62e02ead752ac9a0076.jpg&h=8218dd18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065249_e0e09d780fa06fcb1cb421ab551f85d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065249_e0e09d780fa06fcb1cb421ab551f85d5.jpg&h=e474bba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065250_e0e09d780fa06fcb1cb421ab551f85d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065250_e0e09d780fa06fcb1cb421ab551f85d5.jpg&h=802233ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065421_4081215e71fba825be4383274d06c536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065421_4081215e71fba825be4383274d06c536.jpg&h=dbfb6a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我住嘅瀨戶內町，面向住瀨户內海<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065653_fa25e61f82f3906e1a4028577597288f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065653_fa25e61f82f3906e1a4028577597288f.jpg&h=bffdc840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/065712_93d271faafe53db8028e00c35ee9dff5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F065712_93d271faafe53db8028e00c35ee9dff5.jpg&h=68f92ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，呢到真係好多錦鯉，唔係講笑真係同天星出面堆白鴿無分別<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070001_3f9338f00744d79d1e9c363b4de69c91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070001_3f9338f00744d79d1e9c363b4de69c91.jpg&h=ab4c9b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070102_20105d0f7ddb8d71d75af0c2ae52a835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070102_20105d0f7ddb8d71d75af0c2ae52a835.jpg&h=2801402f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三日就去佐豐島，好多貓。個島唔算大，一日都玩得晒。島上面有200yen shuttle，不過班次好疏下，其實體力好少少又早到可以租單車，我廢冇計啦。5點幾就搭船番高松。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070220_0dc1ecfb8097e63778cca5d55b0fdabd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070220_0dc1ecfb8097e63778cca5d55b0fdabd.jpg&h=57544760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070221_0dc1ecfb8097e63778cca5d55b0fdabd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070221_0dc1ecfb8097e63778cca5d55b0fdabd.jpg&h=bf43d7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070221_8234582ad2d439eba0a70442da87bc3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070221_8234582ad2d439eba0a70442da87bc3c.jpg&h=bd43a5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070322_6ce4c50c424b4a8b00eaa908a0389314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070322_6ce4c50c424b4a8b00eaa908a0389314.jpg&h=b5c3e824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070422_60ee6cdc0b859fd60d160a5e498114bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070422_60ee6cdc0b859fd60d160a5e498114bc.jpg&h=9db00f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070455_0e16f1f35e954f0d737b7c986adae298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070455_0e16f1f35e954f0d737b7c986adae298.jpg&h=3e84a3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070756_70a038f5216fa85f9d857de43313ed8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070756_70a038f5216fa85f9d857de43313ed8e.jpg&h=c74ed9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/070757_70a038f5216fa85f9d857de43313ed8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F070757_70a038f5216fa85f9d857de43313ed8e.jpg&h=2f59497b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7372c3c533e9554405ac6bf821a06943fc92f98d","tid":19520,"uid":36231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:31:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5328b5a74687944c124c9c9dab5d50025804c99f","tid":19520,"uid":28049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:34:56.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 底片喺邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12095a031bb0df8e56a37c9987a425027806de6","tid":19520,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb458dfe0751fb2500e5d90fe639a04c6c45a47","tid":19520,"uid":16262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:39:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b942a3e8b7aacf72fbc796686877be021aa71464","tid":19520,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:49:05.000Z","msg":"正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  留名"},{"pid":"63cc5741e38a75a735bfc3de2f35425bcdf79102","tid":19520,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"第四日去佐阿貝介紹嘅泓人市場，買佐2日jr pass老遠由高松搭去高知，我又廢既訓到十一點先識醒，結果搞到2點幾先上jr，5點先到。不過間燒鰹魚係正既。<br />\n<br />\n第五日就去佐愛媛，今次冇咁廢早佐少少起身，例牌搭兩粒幾鐘去松山，落佐車之後想行一陣，上佐路面電車後，見到松山城就落佐車。見到d錦鯉又影佐幾張，點知部67冇啦啦神佐，過唔到片，呢鋪真係碌柒喇。好彩最後搞番掂，原來係塊反光鏡唔識升起，真係屌鬼搞到我趕唔到班火車去下灘睇日落。去到係度吹風睇月亮，冇啊都係眼睛去旅行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第六日去佐小豆島，今日好好天，又冇咩煙霞。不過小豆島好大，巴士班次又唔夾，所以我地（其實唔係我）剩係揀佐去天使散步道，同寒霞溪。買佐個1000yen 1-day pass，都算方便不過都唔會慳好多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/073622_88333f248269c85bacc3da02f127e182.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F073622_88333f248269c85bacc3da02f127e182.jpg&h=680c038f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/073723_b1761746038b6fcbfea8efe4ee489da9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F073723_b1761746038b6fcbfea8efe4ee489da9.jpg&h=32f80a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/074124_0490af9f7157277f5b5b4b72c852543e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F074124_0490af9f7157277f5b5b4b72c852543e.jpg&h=a7f5bc51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/074225_6a5699ef5ff67719815c3f3dc1d6345a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F074225_6a5699ef5ff67719815c3f3dc1d6345a.jpg&h=1586f9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/074858_7755e1822e73d23bb26b26eb02cb7c2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F074858_7755e1822e73d23bb26b26eb02cb7c2c.jpg&h=93e7a58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/074859_7755e1822e73d23bb26b26eb02cb7c2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F074859_7755e1822e73d23bb26b26eb02cb7c2c.jpg&h=7bf0352f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去唔到橄欖公園都有少少可惜既，因為都想坐掃帚打下卡影張魔女宅急便。不過算啦去旅行姐咁走馬看花做乜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個trip大致上係我柒既planning下都算舒服，不過要去多景點就要chur，因為入夜嘅四國其實都幾靜，都係影佐6筒120就完。值得再戰因為德島嗰d都冇玩過。<br />\n<br />\n有機會再出遊記再分享下<br />\n放低ig比咁多位巴打follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIg: lotussiu<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/lotussiu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flotussiu&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2415bc59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/lotussiu</a>"},{"pid":"c538e4d45142cfaf0c05f1bdbd21dbdf07d59d8b","tid":19520,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 底片喺邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />