img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/141612_404fef54c94fed2678d29a7cb35babb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F141612_404fef54c94fed2678d29a7cb35babb7.jpg&h=12b5369c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係用測光apps測光嘅<br />\n因為我set佐-1ev<br />\n同埋通常都用開f/4-f/8光圈<br />\nIso嗰d冇改都係跟番菲林</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94bab432a87e2a7300357977e4765b94e77eb0e","tid":19520,"uid":46513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"無知一問 其實係咪普通菲林機都影到呢種相？之前買過一次性菲林機已經覺得影得好靚 但唔知點簡一部真係相機嘅菲林機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518d0613f8bad0656953dfe42c769f5543ebb433","tid":19520,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問 其實係咪普通菲林機都影到呢種相？之前買過一次性菲林機已經覺得影得好靚 但唔知點簡一部真係相機嘅菲林機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多因素影響嘅<br />\n以我所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現場環境光源 鏡頭特性 菲林 快門曝光 沖晒掃描過程 後制<br />\n<br />\n全部都有機會影響到出黎嘅效果<br />\n當然咩相機都有機會影到日系相<br />\n一部普通入門canon ae1 nikon fm2都可以<br />\n不過其實我覺得冇咩必要刻意去影呢類相<br />\n只要自己鍾意就得<br />\n<br />\n唔知解唔解答到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d6aee2e6dd420b94dc9a682beaf8173cab6f04","tid":19520,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c9b5885a5d1b955ae279864fdb93a4ee1d6aff","tid":19520,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"be5af67698c1760d6ebde832a7b2b77d56a99817","tid":19520,"uid":46513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無知一問 其實係咪普通菲林機都影到呢種相？之前買過一次性菲林機已經覺得影得好靚 但唔知點簡一部真係相機嘅菲林機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多因素影響嘅<br />\n以我所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現場環境光源 鏡頭特性 菲林 快門曝光 沖晒掃描過程 後制<br />\n<br />\n全部都有機會影響到出黎嘅效果<br />\n當然咩相機都有機會影到日系相<br />\n一部普通入門canon ae1 nikon fm2都可以<br />\n不過其實我覺得冇咩必要刻意去影呢類相<br />\n只要自己鍾意就得<br />\n<br />\n唔知解唔解答到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為本身好中意呢啲style 所以一見到就好想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}